{"type": "article", "id": 24449, "title": "Kvadrat 条纹面料", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-25T07:00:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606144645CsbG24uUfoS7XgdO.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是比利时的时装设计师 Raf Simons 和丹麦纺织品牌 Kvadrat 推出的新品条纹面料。选用非常现代的鲜艳的颜色，多数是用一种颜色进行深浅对比，比如大红和橙红，深蓝和晶蓝，也有一些灰色调和中性色调，在活泼中不失协调。用这种面料来装饰意大利建筑师 Franco Albini 的吊椅时会非常活泼。<a href=\"http://kvadrat.dk/products/new\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144643t5QWZlaM4cjTJqH2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144643wEWtyvZNxYjmHfeh.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144644GgejTWOlEJKymX3n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.82685185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n\n\n"}